ljs-keyword&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; details&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 10px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px;&quot;&gt;python默认编码是ascii，所以print的时候会把中文当ascii处理导致出错&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 10px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px;&quot;&gt;解决办法:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre style=&quot;margin-top: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs cpp&quot; style=&quot;margin: auto; padding: 5px !important; height: auto; line-height: 1.5 !important; vertical-align: middle; display: block; font-family: ''Courier New'', sans-serif !important; font-size: 12px !important; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204) !important; border-radius: 3px !important; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-meta&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 145, 175);&quot;&gt;# coding=utf-8&lt;/span&gt;或者&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-meta&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 145, 175);&quot;&gt;#!/usr/bin/python&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-meta&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 145, 175);&quot;&gt;# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h3 id=&quot;字符连接出现错误&quot; style=&quot;margin: 15px auto 2px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;字符连接出现错误&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;pre style=&quot;margin-top: 10px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; line-he